				<h1>What is ComplimentKarma?</h1>
				<p>
					ComplimentKarma is a cloud based application to Send / Receive Compliments (e.g. Thanks, Kudos, Good Job, Recommendation etc.) To / From your Professional and Personal (i.e. Social) contacts.
			  </p><br />
			  <p>
					Based on the compliments you Send / Receive from your coworkers and other job related external contacts (such as Company Clients, Vendors and Suppliers etc.), your Employer / Manager may choose to reward you with monetary Rewards.
				</p><br />
				<p>
					Based on the number of compliments, you will also earn various virtual Badges, Trophies and Certificates for different Skills. You will build your Proof of Experience, to help you with your future job endeavors. You own your profile even if you switch employers. 
				</p><br />
				<p>
					You can exchange compliments with your Professional contacts and your Personal/Social contacts for personal reasons. That is why you have 2 types of Profiles to keep your Professional and Social activity separate, and let you easily manage the visibility/privacy options of each.
				</p><br />
				<p>
					Employers / Managers can sign-up for advanced functionality to administer employee professional accounts, in addition to advanced analytics and rewards programs.
				</p>
				<h2>Is it Free to use ComplimentKarma?</h2>
				<p>
					Yes, ComplimentKarma is 100% Free to use for all Individuals accounts. You don’t need Credit/Debit card to use your personal account.
				</p><br />
				<p>
					Only those Employers / Managers who want to gain extra functionality to Administer their Employees / Teams, need to pay a nominal monthly fee, based on the number of Users they want to Administer.
				</p>
